com.ibm.team.process.common.advice

Interface IAdvisorInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, IReportInfo

    public interface IAdvisorInfo
extends IReportInfo
    An advisor info reports information for an operation advisor. The information reported has an associated severity and may carry additional advisor-specific data (which can be used by UI presentations and/or quick fixes).

    Factory methods to create advisor infos are available on IAdvisorInfoCollector. Implementors of IOperationAdvisor are passed such a collector when they are run.

    Clients may not implement this interface.

    Since:
    0.6
